column5: This resource identifies the MIME type associated with this output file format. For example "application/pdf". IANA maintains a registry of MIME types, see ?[IANA-mt]
t FontParams describes how fonts SHALL be handled when creating PDL.
PDF specific element for the output. It SHALL NOT be specified unless @MimeType="application/pdf".
Postscript specific element for the output. It SHALL NOT be specified unless @MimeType="application/postscript".
